data.description: Prime location single story brick and stone elevation from Sandlin builders just adjacent to the greenbelt in the growing community of Prairie Oaks. Minutes from the community pool and Lake access! Relax in this recent construction open floor plan featuring a beautiful well-equipped kitchen with quartz countertops and ss appliances, extensive tile flooring, perfect room separation for guest or mother-in-law suite, oversized open great room for living and dining, a home office, three full baths, walk-in Master closet, large back yard for kids and pets. Enjoy the low monthly costs of this energy efficient construction. Ask the agent about our interest rate buy down incentive with accepted contract!
